      "content": "i mean i know i should talk to someone or whatever, but it feels like a lot of effort just to stay in a game i've already lost. there's no point in trying to fix the connection when the signal is just dead. there's a weird kind of peace in thinking about just... not having to try anymore. not having to be \"someone\" for anyone.",
